    "text": "Distiller.com uses cookies that are essential for us to operate the website and that are helpful for us to improve the services. By continuing to browse our website, you agree to first-party and third-party cookies being stored on your device. Learn More About Cookies\nACCEPT\nCANCEL\nSEARCH\nALL SPIRITS\nOUR FAVORITE NON-WHISKEY BOTTLES OF 2022\nThese are our favorite non-whiskey releases from 2022!\nSHOW ME!\nRECENT REVIEWS\nHere's what Distiller users are reviewing right now. Join them\nEAGLE RARE 10 YEAR BOURBON\nBourbon — Kentucky, USA\nLast reviewed by keithallen142\n4.04\n(\n11101\n)\nAdd your review\nCOLONEL E.H. TAYLOR, JR....\nBourbon — Kentucky, USA\nLast reviewed by The-V\n4.31\n(\n17\n)\nAdd your review\nANGEL'S ENVY BOURBON FINISHED...\nBourbon — Kentucky, USA\nLast reviewed by lschulz15\n3.86\n(\n6112\n)\nAdd your review\nCORNER CREEK 10 YEAR BOURBON\nBourbon — Kentucky, USA\nLast reviewed by Zak-Antal\n3.63\n(\n65\n)\nAdd your review\nADVERTISEMENT - CONTINUE READING BELOW\nRemove ads, get access to premium features, and more with DISTILLER PRO\nRECENTLY ADDED\nWOODY CREEK COLORADO GIN\nBased in Basalt, Colorado, Woody Creek Distillers was founded by a group of friends who, after their long careers, wanted to leave a legacy of creating and producing craft spirits. Their Colorado...\n4.55\n(\n5\n)\nAdd your review\nWOODY CREEK POTATO VODKA\nThis farm-to-bottle vodka uses 100% potatoes which are grown on their family farm just outside Aspen, Colorado. The potatoes, after mashing and fermentation, are distilled in their custom...\n4.75\n(\n9\n)\nAdd your review\nWOODY CREEK COLORADO STRAIGHT BOURBON\nThis expression is made using locally grown grain from Colorado. It is matured a minimum of 4 years in heavily charred new American oak. It is bottled at 90 proof.\n3.28\n(\n39\n)\nAdd your review\nSIGN UP FOR THE DISTILLER NEWSLETTER\nFOLLOW US\nDOWNLOAD THE APP\nTo learn more about responsible consumption, please visit Foundation For Advancing Alcohol Responsibility.\nTerms Of Service. ™/© 2022 Distiller Privacy Policy Contact Us Advertise Submit For Review Jobs Frequently Asked Questions",
